    "name": "Arcane Path",
    "steam_appid": 3073480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/fef617abe108c95c5c65ed4c505d260f.webp?t=1760789753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras_big/fef617abe108c95c5c65ed4c505d260f.webp?t=1760789753 width=800 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在一座荒凉破败的城市中醒来，成为一个玩偶，记忆全无。通往王宫的道路在前方，但敌对的自动傀儡和奥术魔像挡在你的去路上。为了到达目的地，你必须面对强大的敌人，他们各自守护着你旅程中的关键之地<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/7ef94adb5eb0191a101fc008dceef861.poster.avif?t=1760789753\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/7ef94adb5eb0191a101fc008dceef861.webm?t=1760789753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/7ef94adb5eb0191a101fc008dceef861.mp4?t=1760789753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场战斗都将考验你对魔法卡牌、神器和技能的运用极限。审慎选择行动，适应敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/8a2ab864fe2f7c2b5957737dc09aab08.poster.avif?t=1760789753\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/8a2ab864fe2f7c2b5957737dc09aab08.webm?t=1760789753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/8a2ab864fe2f7c2b5957737dc09aab08.mp4?t=1760789753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Arcane Path》的每次冒险开始前，你需要从12件神器中选择一件，塑造你的游戏风格。每件神器都赋予独特的状态效果，为初始卡牌带来强力加成，并将主题卡牌加入你的牌组。神器还会影响战斗奖励，确保关键胜利带来符合其主题的卡牌，解锁全新策略与玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/c150aa9ca9b16b06dbaccf8f86a10570.poster.avif?t=1760789753\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/c150aa9ca9b16b06dbaccf8f86a10570.webm?t=1760789753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/c150aa9ca9b16b06dbaccf8f86a10570.mp4?t=1760789753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一本古老的书低语着与12件遗物相连的被遗忘力量，以及启动你探险之旅的神秘力量。它那神秘莫测的书页展示了逝去时代的奇迹，隐约透露出一场令城市沦为废墟的命运仪式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/8a5a6278169fc4159d65b48f453e6d7c.poster.avif?t=1760789753\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/8a5a6278169fc4159d65b48f453e6d7c.webm?t=1760789753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/8a5a6278169fc4159d65b48f453e6d7c.mp4?t=1760789753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >克拉维格——戴着猫头鹰面具的自动人偶，以及她的领袖翡翠神谕者，在你通往魔法之城中心的旅途中为你提供援助。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras/f15661127ffb23e51320ff1d2cd08d87.webp?t=1760789753\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073480/extras_big/f15661127ffb23e51320ff1d2cd08d87.webp?t=1760789753 width=800 height=38 /></span></p>",
